Kab khaulega tera khoon Coke studio India?

Tbh what Pakistan coke studio is doing, i have always dreamt about it, taking own regional folk songs to every house in the way modern people understands it, and not letting people forget how rich our culture is.
You go every where in India you'll see the traditional artist and singers are not even able to run their house.( Few generations back they used to perform for royal people in their palace and now their art is dying). We need to do something to preserve our Art and Culture, we need to move on from shit Desi music factory types labels who release shit songs and get 100milliona of views and likes. 
The problem is with the listeners, once you stop listening to garbage, stop giving them views and likes on shit track and affect their business, they will automatically understand that audience needs quality.
